description: Kryst was born in Michigan and moved to the Carolinas as a child, eventually attended the University of South Carolina. Kryst had a law degree and an MBA from Wake Forest University when she won Miss USA. She was working as an attorney in North Carolina when she entered the 2019 competition. Fellow Miss USA contestant Tianna Tuamoheloa said Kryst "really did just have a light about her"
